          <h3>2026 Example</h3>
          <p><strong>Bǐngwǔ</strong> (<span class="chinese-char">丙午</span>) — Yang Fire Horse. The 43rd combination, basis for <a href="/bazi/">BaZi</a> year pillar calculations.</p>
